suarez mason who contends he has no money 
suarez mason was argentinas most wanted fugitive during his 
three years of freedom before his arrest in january 1987 and is the 
highestranking former military officer currently facing trial by 
the civilian government he was not covered by the amnesty granted 
by the government to lowerranking military officials 
