<TEXT>
the state thats home to the grand canyon 
and the petrified forest will soon acquire another natural wonder 
a spectacular 2mile cavern kept secret for years for fear it 
would be vandalized 
the legislature and gov rose mofford on wednesday rushed to 
enact legislation allowing the state to acquire the cavern 
discovered 14 years ago near benson in southeast arizona 
